      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，流程分几个阶段。首先是同步阶段：payment service在T10ms接收请求，然后做idempotency check和JWT validation，这两个分别对应Groupware_WikiPage和Groupware_ChatRoom的元数据。接着T25ms做wallet balance check，用Groupware_KanbanBoard标记。",
      "elements_involved": [
